# Use MongoDB Atlas for production: https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
# Format: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/dbname?...
# 
# Steps:
# 1. Create cluster at https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
# 2. Create database user with strong password
# 3. Get connection string and fill it here
# 4. Add your deployment IP to IP whitelist
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/ai-learning-assistant?retryWrites=true&w=majority

